---
<BaseLayout
  title={`Web Design ${city} MD | WordPress & SEO | Upcoming Brand`}
  description={`Web design ${city} businesses trust for real Google rankings. Custom WordPress builds, 90+ PageSpeed, fixed pricing. Serving Salisbury, Fruitland, Ocean City, and the Eastern Shore.`}
  canonicalUrl={canonical}
>
  <!-- JSON-LD in head slot -->
  <script slot="head" type="application/ld+json" set:html={jsonLd} />

  <AnnouncementBar />
  <Navigation />

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO
  ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <ServiceHero
    eyebrow='A studio, not a factory'
    pillText='WordPress Specialists · Salisbury, MD'
    h1Lines={[
      { text: 'Salisbury' },
      { text: 'web design that ranks,', type: 'accent' },
      { text: 'converts & keeps working.', type: 'italic' },
    ]}
    lead={`Upcoming Brand is a Maryland-based WordPress web design studio. We design and build custom WordPress websites for <strong>TidalHealth-affiliated medical practices, Delmarva Peninsula contractors, downtown Salisbury restaurants,</strong> Wicomico County law firms, and Eastern Shore small businesses - sites built for the way the Salisbury market actually searches.`}
    formName='salisbury-inquiry'
    trustLines={['Top Rated · Upwork', '400+ projects · 12 countries', 'Remote-first · Zoom · Async']}
    hiddenFields={{ location: 'Salisbury, MD' }}
    formSteps={[
      {
        title: 'Tell us who you are',
        subtitle: 'Just your name and email. 30 seconds.',
        fields: [
          { type: 'text',  name: 'name',  label: 'Your name',     placeholder: 'Jane Smith',       required: true, autocomplete: 'name' },
          { type: 'email', name: 'email', label: 'Email address', placeholder: 'jane@company.com', required: true, autocomplete: 'email' },
        ],
      },
      {
        title: 'About your business',
        subtitle: 'Company and what you do.',
        fields: [
          { type: 'text', name: 'company', label: 'Company or brand', placeholder: 'Smith & Co.', autocomplete: 'organization' },
          { type: 'select', name: 'business_type', label: 'Business type', required: true,
            options: ['Law Firm / Attorney', 'Dental / Medical', 'Real Estate', 'Restaurant / Hospitality', 'Contractor / Trades', 'Nonprofit / Church', 'Ecommerce / Retail', 'Small Business / Startup', 'Other'] },
        ],
      },
      {
        title: 'What you need',
        subtitle: 'Which service and your budget.',
        fields: [
          { type: 'select', name: 'service_interest', label: 'Service interested in', required: true,
            options: ['New WordPress site build', 'Redesign existing site', 'WooCommerce store', 'WordPress SEO services', 'Migration to WordPress', 'Care plan / maintenance', 'SEO audit', 'Not sure yet'] },
          { type: 'select', name: 'budget', label: 'Budget range', required: true,
            options: ['Under $1,500', '$1,500 to $3,500', '$3,500 to $6,000', '$6,000 to $15,000', '$15,000+', 'Not sure yet'] },
        ],
      },
      {
        title: 'Timeline + goal',
        subtitle: 'When you need it and what success looks like.',
        fields: [
          { type: 'select', name: 'timeline', label: 'Timeline', required: true,
            options: ['ASAP, within 4 weeks', 'Standard, 6 to 10 weeks', 'Flexible, 3+ months', 'Just exploring'] },
          { type: 'textarea', name: 'message', label: 'Project goal', placeholder: 'Three sentences. We will ask the rest in the reply.', required: true, rows: 2 },
        ],
      },
    ]}
  />

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════
       DEFINITION
  ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="lp-definition section-pad-sm" aria-labelledby="def-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="lp-def-inner">

        <div class="lp-def-left">
          <span class="lp-def-label mono-xs">Definition</span>
          <h2 class="lp-def-heading" id="def-heading">What is custom WordPress web design?</h2>
          <div class="lp-def-amber-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="lp-def-right">
          <p class="lp-def-body">Custom WordPress web design means building your site from a blank canvas on WordPress CMS - not installing a $59 theme already running on 40,000 other businesses. For a Salisbury contractor handling both historic downtown renovation and Ocean City beach property work, that means a quote request form that actually submits, HomeAndConstructionBusiness schema, and service area pages covering Fruitland, Berlin, and Cambridge. For a TidalHealth-affiliated specialist drawing patients from three counties, it means HIPAA-aware contact forms, Physician schema, and appointment pages that rank for condition-specific searches across a 3-county Eastern Shore region. For a Wicomico County attorney serving agricultural landowners, it means multi-step intake forms, LegalService schema, and attorney profile pages that rank for the competitive legal searches Eastern Shore clients use before calling any office. You own the code outright with no monthly platform fee. Every build ships with 90+ PageSpeed, JSON-LD schema matched to your exact business type, and all three Core Web Vitals passing before the DNS transfers.</p>

